  "description": "雨姗AI收银助手创味菜 - 智能餐饮服务系统，支持语音点餐、文字聊天、AI Agent接入、完整订单生命周期",
  "main": "lambda/server.js",
  "scripts": {
    "start": "node lambda/server.js",
    "dev": "nodemon lambda/server.js",
